@startuml
title Diagrama de Comunicación - Gestión de Asistencias
actor User
participant "AsistenciaController" as AC
participant "Horario Model" as HDB
participant "Asistencia Model / DB" as ADB
participant "AuditLog" as Audit

User -> AC: POST /horarios/{horario}/asistencias (form)
AC -> HDB: validate horario and window
HDB --> AC: ok
AC -> ADB: create asistencia
ADB --> AC: asistencia
AC -> Audit: create log
AC --> User: redirect /horarios/{horario}/asistencias
@enduml
